net.ligreto.data
Class DataProviderRow

java.lang.Object
  net.ligreto.data.DataProviderRow
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<DataProviderRow>
public class DataProviderRow
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<DataProviderRow>

This is the row of the data provider. This class is mainly used to store the rows for sorting and to identify the rows with duplicate key columns.

Author:
Julius Stroffek
